### 1. Request OTP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/mobile/auth/request-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobileno": "9876543210"
}

### 2. Verify OTP (Use OTP from Step 1 response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/mobile/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobileno": "9876543210",
  "otp": "REPLACE_WITH_OTP_FROM_STEP_1"
}

### 3. Resend OTP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/mobile/auth/resend-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobileno": "9876543210"
}

### 4. Validate Token (Use token from Step 2 response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/mobile/auth/validate-token
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN_FROM_STEP_2

### 5. Get Orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mobile/orders/9876543210

### 6. Get Order Details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mobile/orders/details/123911

### 7. Track Order
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mobile/orders/track/123911
